Usage: SET TIMESTAMP <format description for timestamps>
  Setting the variable allows you to alter the appearance of
  timestamps.  Certain special characters are recognized in
  this format line and replaced with various bits of status line
  information.  Each of these special characters is preceeded by
  a '%'.  Please read the strftime man page on your system to
  determine which characters are supported.
